thread.title: Alanna O'Sullivan

author: Alanna O'Sullivan
title: Alanna O'Sullivan
text: Great customer service, ordered on Saturday, order was ready for collection on Monday, collected on Tuesday. When I got there, Colin Mooney greeted me and asked for the order number, once I gave him that he listed my ordered parts, left for less than a minute, got my order and helped me out the door. I had a great experience with MicksGarage!
